descriptionNullable:
Hey Kagglers!! Wanted to share this dataset that I came across on the Internet.
It's well-maintained and is great for Data Visualization tasks. You can derive various insights such as Countries Where Orders are less so as to target them with expansion strategies. Which customers are frequent buyers and then target the higher revenue generating customers and ensure that they remain satisfied with their products.. View time series data for a particular year figure out seasonal trends and  dig deeper into why these trends occur. Gain insights on the demand for the products. Feel free to even use it for training a time series model to forecast Sales or for a clustering problem to find out different types of customers.

Happy Learning and Please do upvote if u like it , goes a long way ThankYou!!
